title: New 'Star Wars' trailer on 'Monday Night Football,' online
text:
> Top News New 'Star Wars' trailer on 'Monday Night Football,' online This undated photo provided by Disney shows the poster for the new film, "Star Wars: The Force Awakens." "Star Wars" fans eagerly await the latest trailer for "The Force Awakens," airing during halftime of "Monday Night Football," on Oct. 19, 2015. The game starts at 5:15 p.m. PDT/8:15 p.m. EDT. (Disney via AP)
